title: League of Legends Game Length Predictor
description: Performed linear regression on League of Legends game data to predict game length based on various in-game statistics.

title: San Diego MTS Bus Wait Time Analysis
description: Analyzed San Diego MTS bus wait times using historical data to identify patterns and improve scheduling efficiency.

title: Loan Applications
description: Developed a machine learning model to predict loan application outcomes based on applicant data, improving approval accuracy and reducing risk.

title: Language Model
description: Created a custom language model using deep learning techniques to generate human-like text, enhancing natural language processing capabilities.

title: Imagine Converter
description: Developed an image-to-text converter that utilizes advanced OCR techniques to extract text from images, facilitating data entry and document digitization.

title: Simple Number Recognizer
description: Built a simple number recognition system using machine learning algorithms to identify handwritten digits, demonstrating basic image classification techniques.

title: Taylor Swift Song Recommender
description: Developed a song recommendation system using collaborative filtering techniques to suggest Taylor Swift songs based on user preferences and listening history.

title: Meoterite Landing Simulator
description: Created a simulation of meteorite landings using physics-based modeling to study impact dynamics and predict landing sites, contributing to planetary science research.
